trans-unit.source: Provides a read-only collection of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Fornece uma coleção somente leitura de <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer"> </xref> objetos.

trans-unit.source: The TransformerTypeCollection class represents a read-only collection of objects, typically used by <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZone> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> objects to manage sets of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> objects.
trans-unit.target: A classe TransformerTypeCollection representa uma coleção somente leitura de objetos, normalmente usado por <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZone>e <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>objetos para gerenciar conjuntos de <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer>objetos.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZone>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control uses a TransformerTypeCollection collection to keep a list of available <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> objects on a page, whereas a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZone> object uses a TransformerTypeCollection collection to track the available <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> objects that it contains.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>controle usa uma coleção de TransformerTypeCollection para manter uma lista de disponíveis <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer>objetos em uma página, enquanto um <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZone>objeto usa uma coleção de TransformerTypeCollection para rastrear disponíveis <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer>objetos que ele contém.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZone> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: Although the TransformerTypeCollection collection is read-only, you can make programmatic changes to the properties of the underlying controls referenced in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Embora a coleção TransformerTypeCollection é somente leitura, você pode fazer alterações programáticas para as propriedades dos controles subjacentes referenciado na coleção.
